| No rate limiting | High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No error handler | High | Add error middleware |
| Hardcoded PII in route | High | Add auth + remove hardcoded data |
| No body size limit | Medium | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No CORS policy | Medium | Add `cors` with origin whitelist |
| Hardcoded port | Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| No input validation | Medium | Add `express-validator` |

